    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="修改-bash-profile立即生效的三种方法"><a href="#修改-bash-profile立即生效的三种方法" class="headerlink" title="修改.bash_profile立即生效的三种方法"></a>修改.bash_profile立即生效的三种方法</h2><ol>
<li><code>. .bash_profile</code></li>
<li><code>source .bash_profile</code></li>
<li><code>exec bash --login</code></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="Easy-way-to-determine-virtualization-technology"><a href="#Easy-way-to-determine-virtualization-technology" class="headerlink" title="Easy way to determine virtualization technology"></a>Easy way to determine virtualization technology</h2><ul>
<li><p><code>dmidecode -s system-product-name</code></p>
</li>
<li><p>Virtualization technolgies </p>
<ul>
<li><p>VMware Workstation</p>
<figure class="highlight delphi"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">root@localhost:~# dmidecode -s system-product-<span class="keyword">name</span></div><div class="line">VMware <span class="keyword">Virtual</span> <span class="keyword">Platform</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>VirtualBox</p>
<figure class="highlight elixir"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">root<span class="variable">@localhost</span><span class="symbol">:~</span><span class="comment"># dmidecode -s system-product-name</span></div><div class="line">VirtualBox</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>Qemu with KVM</p>
<figure class="highlight elixir"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">root<span class="variable">@localhost</span><span class="symbol">:~</span><span class="comment"># dmidecode -s system-product-name</span></div><div class="line">KVM</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>Qemu (emulated)</p>
<figure class="highlight elixir"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">root<span class="variable">@localhost</span><span class="symbol">:~</span><span class="comment"># dmidecode -s system-product-name</span></div><div class="line">Bochs</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>References<br>  <a href="http://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/89714/easy-way-to-determine-virtualization-technology" target="_blank" rel="external">linux - Easy way to determine virtualization technology - Unix &amp; Linux Stack Exchange</a></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="CentOS-7-设置静态IP"><a href="#CentOS-7-设置静态IP" class="headerlink" title="CentOS 7 设置静态IP"></a>CentOS 7 设置静态IP</h2><ol>
<li>编辑配置文件:<br> <code>root@localhost:~# vim /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-enp0s3</code></li>
<li><p>修改以下配置项:</p>
 <figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attr">BOOTPROTO</span>=<span class="string">"static"</span> #dhcp改为static </div><div class="line"><span class="attr">ONBOOT</span>=<span class="string">"yes"</span> #开机启用本配置</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">IPADDR</span>=<span class="number">192.168</span>.<span class="number">5.192</span> #静态IP</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">GATEWAY</span>=<span class="number">192.168</span>.<span class="number">4.1</span> #默认网关</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">NETMASK</span>=<span class="number">255.255</span>.<span class="number">252.0</span> #子网掩码</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>修改后的配置:<br> <code>root@localhost:~# cat /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-enp0s3</code></p>
 <figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attr">TYPE</span>=<span class="string">"Ethernet"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">BOOTPROTO</span>=<span class="string">"static"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">DEFROUTE</span>=<span class="string">"yes"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">PEERDNS</span>=<span class="string">"yes"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">PEERROUTES</span>=<span class="string">"yes"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">IPV4_FAILURE_FATAL</span>=<span class="string">"no"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">IPV6INIT</span>=<span class="string">"yes"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">IPV6_AUTOCONF</span>=<span class="string">"yes"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">IPV6_DEFROUTE</span>=<span class="string">"yes"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">IPV6_PEERDNS</span>=<span class="string">"yes"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">IPV6_PEERROUTES</span>=<span class="string">"yes"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">IPV6_FAILURE_FATAL</span>=<span class="string">"no"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">IPV6_ADDR_GEN_MODE</span>=<span class="string">"stable-privacy"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">NAME</span>=<span class="string">"enp0s3"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">UUID</span>=<span class="string">"9281a4f6-b04e-4007-8af0-b05a69e6a5aa"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">DEVICE</span>=<span class="string">"enp0s3"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">ONBOOT</span>=<span class="string">"yes"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">IPADDR</span>=<span class="number">192.168</span>.<span class="number">5.192</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">GATEWAY</span>=<span class="number">192.168</span>.<span class="number">4.1</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">NETMASK</span>=<span class="number">255.255</span>.<span class="number">252.0</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>重启网络服务:<br> <code>root@localhost:~# service network restart</code></p>
</li>
<li>查看修改后的网络信息:<br> <code>root@localhost:~# ip addr</code> <figure class="highlight pf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="number">1</span>: lo: <span class="variable">&lt;LOOPBACK,UP,LOWER_UP&gt;</span> mtu <span class="number">65536</span> qdisc noqueue <span class="keyword">state</span> UNKNOWN qlen <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line">    link/loopback <span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">00</span> brd <span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">00</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">inet</span> <span class="number">127.0</span>.<span class="number">0.1</span>/<span class="number">8</span> scope host lo</div><div class="line">       valid_lft forever preferred_lft forever</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">inet6</span> ::<span class="number">1</span>/<span class="number">128</span> scope host</div><div class="line">       valid_lft forever preferred_lft forever</div><div class="line"><span class="number">2</span>: enp0s3: <span class="variable">&lt;BROADCAST,MULTICAST,UP,LOWER_UP&gt;</span> mtu <span class="number">1500</span> qdisc pfifo_fast <span class="keyword">state</span> UP qlen <span class="number">1000</span></div><div class="line">    link/ether <span class="number">08</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">27</span>:<span class="number">79</span>:<span class="number">22</span>:ab brd ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">inet</span> <span class="number">192.168</span>.<span class="number">5.192</span>/<span class="number">22</span> brd <span class="number">192.168</span>.<span class="number">7.255</span> scope <span class="keyword">global</span> enp0s3</div><div class="line">       valid_lft forever preferred_lft forever</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">inet6</span> fe80::<span class="number">3723</span>:<span class="number">8466</span>:a91:fc59/<span class="number">64</span> scope link</div><div class="line">       valid_lft forever preferred_lft forever</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
]]></content>
    
